wikipedia_page.main: Wasteland is a 2013 zombie horror film directed by Tom Wadlow and written by Tommy Draper. The film was released 23 October 2013 in France and was released to DVD in the United States and Germany, through Midnight Releasing and Maritim Pictures, respectively.
